<a href="../../d7/d46/a00002.php">Go to the documentation of this file.</a><div class="fragment"><div class="line"><a name="l00001"></a><span class="lineno">    1</span>&#160;&lt;div <span class="keywordtype">id</span>=<span class="stringliteral">&quot;presentation&quot;</span>&gt;</div><div class="line"><a name="l00002"></a><span class="lineno">    2</span>&#160;&lt;div&gt;</div><div class="line"><a name="l00003"></a><span class="lineno">    3</span>&#160;  &lt;img src=<span class="stringliteral">&quot;design/img/presentation.jpg&quot;</span> alt=<span class="stringliteral">&quot;un chien en costume de hot dog&quot;</span>&gt;</div><div class="line"><a name="l00004"></a><span class="lineno">    4</span>&#160;&lt;/div&gt;</div><div class="line"><a name="l00005"></a><span class="lineno">    5</span>&#160;&lt;div&gt;</div><div class="line"><a name="l00006"></a><span class="lineno">    6</span>&#160;&lt;h1&gt;C<span class="stringliteral">&#39;est quoi HOT DOG QUIZ ?&lt;/h1&gt;</span></div><div class="line"><a name="l00007"></a><span class="lineno">    7</span>&#160;<span class="stringliteral">&lt;p&gt;HOT DOG QUIZ, C&#39;</span>est le meilleur <a class="code" href="../../dd/da2/a00019.php#a8c9d97109099b8ce02792d0c4abd3ae3">jeu</a> du web de l<span class="stringliteral">&#39;année 2018. Ce jeux est inspiré  de Burger Quiz qui est un jeu télévisé inventé par Alain Chabat</span></div><div class="line"><a name="l00008"></a><span class="lineno">    8</span>&#160;<span class="stringliteral">  et Kader Aoun, diffusé sur Canal+ en quotidien du 27 août 2001 au 5 juillet 2002 à 20 h 5 en clair, puis, depuis le 25 avril 2018, sur TMC</span></div><div class="line"><a name="l00009"></a><span class="lineno">    9</span>&#160;<span class="stringliteral">  en hebdomadaire en première partie de soirée. Le jeu est produit par la société de production Chez Wam, puis par la société R&amp;G Production</span></div><div class="line"><a name="l00010"></a><span class="lineno">   10</span>&#160;<span class="stringliteral">  et réalisée par Jérôme Revon. L&#39;</span>émission a principalement été présentée par Alain Chabat.Le concept de l<span class="stringliteral">&#39;émission consiste à répondre à des</span></div><div class="line"><a name="l00011"></a><span class="lineno">   11</span>&#160;<span class="stringliteral">  questions plus ou moins loufoques afin d&#39;</span>atteindre les 25 points, appelés miams, avant l<span class="stringliteral">&#39;équipe adverse.</span></div><div class="line"><a name="l00012"></a><span class="lineno">   12</span>&#160;<span class="stringliteral">&lt;/p&gt;</span></div><div class="line"><a name="l00013"></a><span class="lineno">   13</span>&#160;<span class="stringliteral">&lt;/div&gt;</span></div><div class="line"><a name="l00014"></a><span class="lineno">   14</span>&#160;<span class="stringliteral">&lt;/div&gt;</span></div><div class="line"><a name="l00015"></a><span class="lineno">   15</span>&#160;<span class="stringliteral"></span></div><div class="line"><a name="l00016"></a><span class="lineno">   16</span>&#160;<span class="stringliteral">&lt;div id=&quot;accueilPerso&quot;&gt;</span></div><div class="line"><a name="l00017"></a><span class="lineno">   17</span>&#160;<span class="stringliteral">  &lt;form method=&quot;post&quot; action=&quot; jeu.php&quot; target=&quot;_self&quot;&gt;</span></div><div class="line"><a name="l00018"></a><span class="lineno">   18</span>&#160;<span class="stringliteral">    &lt;div id=&quot;blockBoutons&quot;&gt;</span></div><div class="line"><a name="l00019"></a><span class="lineno">   19</span>&#160;<span class="stringliteral">      &lt;button id=&quot;boutonModifier&quot;&gt;Modifier son profil&lt;/button&gt;</span></div><div class="line"><a name="l00020"></a><span class="lineno">   20</span>&#160;<span class="stringliteral">      &lt;button id=&quot;boutonCreer&quot;&gt;Créer une partie&lt;/button&gt;</span></div><div class="line"><a name="l00021"></a><span class="lineno">   21<